Job Description 
 GENERAL SCOPE & SUMMARY 
Looking for a great company to leverage your voice engineering skills? Ready to advance your career and work with real cloud networks? If you would enjoy working with carrier-grade and enterprise voice deployments, then we want to talk. 
Aspect is looking for a Voice Engineer to join the Cloud Operations team. We are looking for the best candidates interested in working with a company offering top-tier employee benefits and those who want the opportunity to work with our cloud technologies. The candidate weâ€™re searching for will be experienced with VoIP troubleshooting, as well as voice system configurations. 
Duties and Responsibilities: 
Architect, deploy and maintain Ribbon (Sonus) Session Border Controllers 
Identify, troubleshoot, and resolve VoIP performance problems 
Work with carriers to track down and resolve carrier related issues 
Interoperability testing for new carriers or customers 
Work with Senior Engineers on new projects or features. 
Troubleshoot any reported voice issues on voice backbone. 
Help organize and maintain internal systems to track issues and resolutions 
